Name: Moon Runner
About the game: You are a Moon Runner - a special unit dispatched by Astral Cortex Industries and tasked with finding the monoliths on this moon. Pick up items scattered across the surface and use them to traverse and survive this lunar landscape. Gameplay and features: - Survival, traversal and action gameplay. - Moody and atmospheric lunar setting. - A spherical level design with map system, inventory, side objectives and a score entry in a global leaderboard.
